    "Zhuang et al. [243] investigated edge inference for MC-assisted ISAC systems, where multiple ISAC devices sensed the targets from different directions and uploaded their sensing data to an edge server for training the AI model.",
    "They optimized the sensing power allocation and the transceiver to maximize the task-oriented performance criterion.",
    "However, the EC-aided AI-enabled ISAC encounters two main challenges.",
    "On the one hand, the data offload raises severe security concerns, especially when the data contains the sensitive information.",
    "On the other hand, integrating EC into the AI-enabled ISAC network leads to complicated trade-offs among communication, sensing, and computation."
